profile: SWS is locally owned and operated and has been serving Northumberland County since 1991. We specialize in whole home water treatment, are licensed by the Ministry of Environment to perform well & pump services, and we offer 24 hour emergency service. Our store location showcases Roto Spa Hot Tubs and has 4 self-fill Reverse Osmosis drinking stations.
